---
---

<section class="relative overflow-hidden">
  <div
    aria-hidden="true"
    class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_top,_#FFEEFA_0%,_#FFFFFF_55%)]"
  ></div>
  <div
    aria-hidden="true"
    class="absolute -top-32 right-[-120px] -z-10 h-[420px] w-[420px] rounded-full bg-primary-200/60 blur-3xl"
  ></div>
  <div
    aria-hidden="true"
    class="absolute -bottom-40 left-[-160px] -z-10 h-[480px] w-[480px] rounded-full bg-[#EBE9FE]/80 blur-3xl"
  ></div>

  <div class="container-content grid items-center gap-12 py-16 md:py-24 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-16">
    <div class="animate-fade-up">
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-primary-100 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-primary-600">
        <span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary-600"></span>
        영어 단어 학습, 다시 즐겁게
      </span>

      <h1 class="mt-5 text-4xl font-extrabold leading-[1.15] tracking-tight text-ink-900 md:text-5xl lg:text-[56px]">
        망각 직전,<br />
        <span class="text-primary-600">다시 만나는 단어.</span>
      </h1>

      <p class="mt-6 max-w-xl text-base leading-relaxed text-ink-700 md:text-lg">
        SM2 알고리즘 기반 자동 복습 스케줄과 게임 같은 업적 시스템.<br class="hidden md:block" />
        헤이보카가 외운 단어를 잊지 않게 챙겨드려요.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-9 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3">
        <a href="#download" class="btn-primary">
          앱 다운로드
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6" />
          </svg>
        </a>
        <a href="#features" class="btn-ghost">특장점 살펴보기</a>
      </div>

      <dl class="mt-10 grid max-w-md grid-cols-3 gap-4 border-t border-ink-100 pt-6">
        <div>
          <dt class="text-xs text-ink-500">학습 알고리즘</dt>
          <dd class="mt-1 text-base font-bold text-ink-900">SM2</dd>
        </div>
        <div>
          <dt class="text-xs text-ink-500">지원 플랫폼</dt>
          <dd class="mt-1 text-base font-bold text-ink-900">iOS · Android</dd>
        </div>
        <div>
          <dt class="text-xs text-ink-500">소셜 로그인</dt>
          <dd class="mt-1 text-base font-bold text-ink-900">Google · Apple</dd>
        </div>
      </dl>
    </div>

    <div class="relative mx-auto w-full max-w-[480px] animate-fade-up">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 translate-y-6 scale-95 rounded-[48px] bg-primary-200/40 blur-2xl"></div>
      <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-[40px] bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-100 to-white p-8 shadow-[0_30px_60px_-20px_rgba(255,112,212,0.35)]">
        <img
          src="/images/HeyCharacter.png"
          alt="헤이보카 캐릭터"
          width="640"
          height="640"
          class="mx-auto h-auto w-full max-w-[320px] animate-float-y"
          loading="eager"
          decoding="async"
        />
        <div class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-3 gap-3">
          <img src="/images/AttendanceKing.png" alt="" width="120" height="120" class="h-auto w-full rounded-2xl bg-white p-2 shadow-sm" loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/images/MemorizedKing.png" alt="" width="120" height="120" class="h-auto w-full rounded-2xl bg-white p-2 shadow-sm" loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/images/PerseveranceKing.png" alt="" width="120" height="120" class="h-auto w-full rounded-2xl bg-white p-2 shadow-sm" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
